he said. <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> can include with the statute a provision that would speed court review, he said. The <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Judiciary </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Committee </ORGANIZATION> is expected to meet on flag legislation later this week and <PERSON> Foley </PERSON> said he still intends to bring a statute to the full <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> before the August recess. <PERSON> Foley </PERSON> said he might not be able to block a <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> vote on the constitutional amemdment, but indicated he'd at least like to let the <ORGANIZATION> Senate </ORGANIZATION> act first, which it is now scheduled to do in October. `` The danger is not only amending the Constitution without necessity, it's lowering the level of resistance in the <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> and the country to amendments to the Constitution and most particularly to the First Amendment, which is the basis as we all know of speech, religious and press liberty,'' he said.
