<FIRST>s a BC-APN--TheBaca-Projects Adv06   07-24 0213</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-APN--The Baca-Projects, Adv 06,0222</SECOND>
<HEAD>$Adv06</HEAD>
<HEAD>AGENCIES AND RADIO OUT</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Sunday, Aug. 6</HEAD>
<HEAD>With BC-APN--The Baca</HEAD>
<TEXT>
